From: HunyuanOCR-ncnn contributors
Subject: [PATCH 4/4] Vulkan InnerProduct M=1 vector dispatch
Upstream: https://github.com/Tencent/ncnn
License: BSD 3-Clause
Local-Note: Route two-dimensional single-row InnerProduct inputs through the
 existing Vulkan vector pipelines while preserving the matrix-shaped output.
 Use ncnn packing conversion when the vector output pack axis changes.
 Covers both fp32 and int8 paths with ncnn regression tests.
diff --git a/src/layer/vulkan/innerproduct_vulkan.cpp b/src/layer/vulkan/innerproduct_vulkan.cpp
